<i>adverb</i>: 황당히 [황당히], 턱없이 [터겁씨], 터무니없이 [터무니업씨], 어처구니없이 [어처구니업씨], 어이없이 [어이업씨] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square"><li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>황당히 [황당히]</dt><br>
<dd>absurdly; ridiculously</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동 등이 진실하지 않고 터무니없이.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of one's words or acts being insincere and absurd.</dd><br>
<dt>턱없이 [터겁씨]</dt><br>
<dd>1. groundlessly; unfoundedly</dd><br>
<dd>이치에 맞지 않거나, 그럴만한 근거가 전혀 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>Out of reason or without any grounds.</dd><br>
<dd>2. absurdly; ridiculously</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 수준이나 분수에 맞지 않게.</dd><br>
<dd>In an excessive degree for a certain level or situation.</dd><br>
<dt>터무니없이 [터무니업씨]</dt><br>
<dd>absurdly; unreasonably</dd><br>
<dd>황당하고 믿음성이 없어 전혀 근거가 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>Without a foundation, as something is ridiculous and lacks credibility.</dd><br>
<dt>어처구니없이 [어처구니업씨]</dt><br>
<dd>absurdly; ridiculously; preposterously</dd><br>
<dd>너무 뜻밖의 일을 당해서 기가 막히는 듯하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of being dumbfounded due to an extremely unexpected occurrence.</dd><br>
<dt>어이없이 [어이업씨]</dt><br>
<dd>absurdly; ridiculously; preposterously</dd><br>
<dd>너무 뜻밖의 일을 당해서 기가 막히는 듯하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of being dumbfounded due to an extremely unexpected occurrence.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>